text: The Estonia national under-18 and under-19 basketball team is the national representative for Estonia in international under-18 and under-19 basketball competitions. They are controlled by the Eesti Korvpalliliit. The team competes at the FIBA U18 European Championship, with the opportunity to qualify for the FIBA Under-19 World Cup. ==See also== *Estonia national basketball team *Estonia national under-17 basketball team ==References== ==External links== *Official website *FIBA profile Category:National sports teams of Estonia Category:National under-18 basketball teams Category:National under-19 basketball teams
